DISCLAIMER

The synthetic regulatory clauses in this repository are NOT official legal text
and do NOT reproduce any official regulatory document verbatim. They are
purpose-built research artefacts for evaluating executable reasoning systems.

LEXON is a research prototype for executable regulatory information reasoning.
It does not provide legal advice and does not determine legal compliance.
